                <p>Adnigam.com, is an online marketplace created for local offline retailers to promote them as the best sellers in the vicinity. We enable them to showcase and sell their products/services to the consumers using our website and mobile apps. We provide the best and state- of- the- art technology platform which offers seamless integration to all the stakeholders. We assure the vendors and consumers secured and hassle free transactions through the most reliable and trusted payment gateway.</p>
                <br/><p>Adnigam Pvt Ltd(Formerly known as Adrobe Networks Pvt Ltd), India's first ad-commerce company, was incorporated in the year 2015 to create one of the best platforms which can fill the wider gaps between offline and online markets. We provide e-commerce solutions to the vendors/sellers who require an omni-channel business model at an affordable price point.</p>
                
